advancement.antsportation.mod_for_ants: What is this? A mod for ants?
advancement.antsportation.mod_for_ants.d: Get an Ant Jar and start your ant adventures!
advancement.antsportation.small_infantry: How can you dare hit an ant.
advancement.antsportation.wrapping_up.de: Make a box and start packing items.
boxer_tooltip.antsportation.eject_when: The percentage a box needs to be filled in order to allow extraction. 0 disables this functionality
boxer_tooltip.antsportation.redstone_con: Decides when box extraction should be allowed, based on redstone signal. Use 'DISABLED' in order to keep the box locked until the ejection percent is hit.
jei.antsportation.ant_jar: Used for decoration and storing Ant Queens.
jei.antsportation.ant_nest: Generated randomly throughout forest biomes. Break them with Silk Touch otherwise you might get hurt!
jei.antsportation.box: Used to package items for ant transportation. Use Boxers / Unboxers for inserting and extracting items.
jei.antsportation.boxer: Machine used to pack items into boxes.
jei.antsportation.chunkloading_marker: A special type of marker that chunk loads the chunk it is in.
jei.antsportation.marker: Used to create a path for ants to follow.
jei.antsportation.unboxer: Machine used to unpack items from boxes.
message.antsportation.too_close_marker: The marker placed at %s is too close to the marker at %s. Consider spreading the markers for optimal results.
patchouli.antsportation.landing_text:
$(#800080)Welcome to Antsportation, ! This book will guide you through the mod and show you how to use ants to make cool item transportation systems!
Check out $(l:antsportation:other/setup_item_transport)Setting up item transportation$()$(#800080) on how to get started!
tooltip.item.antsportation.chunk_loading: This server has disabled Chunk Loading Markers!
tooltip.item.antsportation.has_ant: This jar contains an Ant Queen
tooltip.item.antsportation.speed_upgrade: Insert in a Boxer in order to make it faster.
Increases energy usage: %s more FE / tick
tooltip.item.antsportation.transportable: This item can be transported directly by ants.
top.antsportation.ticks_until_spawn: Ticks until a new ant is spawned: %s
